 6→ * 2. Selecting top N within token budget
 7→ * 3. Building <brain-context> XML block
 8→ * 4. Injecting into system prompt (string or array form)
 9→ *
10→ * All functions are pure -- no IO, no side effects.
11→ * The orchestration (embedding, cache, DB queries) lives in the proxy route.
